    "question_id" : 15111420,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To account for other digits beside Latin/English (aka Western Arabic digits):</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>var regex = &quot;\\\\p{javaDigit}+&quot;; // Same as &quot;\\\\p{Nd}+&quot;\n&quot;1234۱۲۳۴&quot;.matches(regex); // true\n</code></pre>\n<p>For Kotlin:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-kotlin prettyprint-override\"><code>&quot;1234۱۲۳۴&quot;.all(Char::isDigit) // true\n// OR\n&quot;1234۱۲۳۴&quot; matches Regex(&quot;\\\\p{javaDigit}&quot;) // Same as &quot;\\\\p{Nd}&quot;\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
